	<description>Template package for creating notepadplusplus plugin packages  
  
## Template Properties

- `PLUGIN_NAME` - Optional property for using this template. This plugin name must be the name of the plugin dll as well.  
   For example if you dll is named: 'BetterMultiSelection.dll' then the plugin name should be: **BetterMultiSelection**.  
   Default: package-id.

## Usage
- Example 1:  `choco new bettermultiselection -t notepadplusplus-plugin`  
- Example 2:  `choco new myplugin -t notepadplusplus-plugin PLUGIN_NAME="DllPluginFileName"`  
